    Combination of a host and port.

    Represents an MRSP URI.
    MsrpUriComparator

    Represents one outgoing MSRP message broken into multiple SEND MsrpRequest chunks.

    Represents one MSRP session.

Package org.dellroad.msrp Description

Top level package for the msrp4j Java library.

The main class is Msrp. Each instance represents an MSRP protocol stack.
